  ('cbf5c85c-9ac2-5a1b-bb95-1929253d8e7c', '3385d4a5-b4c2-5331-a7a9-53a03f3f4869', '2ee55359-b5ce-5fa2-8710-cb048521502a', '100002785496', 'Audio page: 1 st audio copy: 2 nd audio copy – this is your final listening attempt: The questions for this audio are below: At the start, they both agree they like to go hiking in order to… Hiking anywhere can be challenging. It is clear they think so because they talk about the need to... Regarding unexpected situations, what do they say to do first? Based on what they say, what can we be most confident about? I have listened to the full audio.', 'Listening comprehension', 'Item set home pages (audios)', 'D1', 0, 'active'),
