  ('36cd52f7-0c37-5cb0-aea3-5e59978b9f33', '3385d4a5-b4c2-5331-a7a9-53a03f3f4869', '2ee55359-b5ce-5fa2-8710-cb048521502a', '100002785514', 'Audio page: 1 st audio copy: 2 nd audio copy – this is your final listening attempt: The questions for this audio are below: According to Dr. Lee, what is the main benefit of using AI in research? What is Dr. Lee’s main concern in trusting AI systems? How does Dr. Lee feel AI will impact jobs? How does Dr. Lee respond to suggestions that AI could replace research jobs? I have listened to the full audio.', 'Listening comprehension', 'Item set home pages (audios)', 'D1', 0, 'active'),
